---
---

<section id="features" class="features">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-tag">Why Unbound?</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Built for the <span class="gradient-text">Total War</span></h2>
      <p class="section-desc">No VPNs. No proxies. Just raw packet-level obfuscation that keeps your internet at full speed.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🧠</div>
        <h3>Smart Multidisorder</h3>
        <p>Breaks TLS ClientHello into fragments sent out of order. DPI can't assemble the puzzle, but target servers handle it easily. <strong>100% bypass</strong> with zero connection drops.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
        <h3>Zero Speed Loss</h3>
        <p>Your traffic doesn't route through foreign servers. Unlike VPNs, your speed stays at maximum. Only blocked domains get modified — banks and government sites work normally.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🎯</div>
        <h3>One-Click Auto-Tune</h3>
        <p>Hit "Auto-Tune" and Unbound parallel-tests profiles on YouTube, Discord, Telegram, Instagram, Twitter, RuTracker. Smart scoring prioritizes profiles that unblock everything at once.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🔒</div>
        <h3>Open Source & Free</h3>
        <p>GPL-3.0 licensed. Every line of code is auditable. All dependencies — Lua scripts, WinDivert drivers, winws2 binary — are embedded in a single executable.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🛡️</div>
        <h3>Conflict Detection</h3>
        <p>Automatically detects conflicting tools — GoodbyeDPI, Zapret, OpenVPN, Cloudflare WARP, ExpressVPN, NordVPN — that could interfere with WinDivert.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🚀</div>
        <h3>Silent Auto-Start</h3>
        <p>Registers with Windows Task Scheduler for silent system tray startup. No UAC pop-ups, no console windows. Set it and forget it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.features {
  padding: 8rem 2rem;
  position: relative;
}

.container {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.section-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 4rem;
}

.section-tag {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
  background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1);
  border: 1px solid rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2);
  border-radius: 100px;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #667eea;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.section-title {
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
  font-weight: 800;
  color: #fff;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  letter-spacing: -1px;
}

.section-desc {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  max-width: 600px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.features-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1.5rem;
}

.feature-card {
  padding: 2rem;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  border-radius: 16px;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.feature-card:hover {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
  border-color: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
}

.feature-icon {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.feature-card h3 {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #fff;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}

.feature-card p {
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  line-height: 1.7;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
}

.feature-card p strong {
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .features-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }
}

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .features-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  .features {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
  }
}
</style>
